102
00:07:21,189 --> 00:07:22,799
Bagaimana jika kita hanya berdua?

103
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:26,200
Hanya kita berdua?

104
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:32,700
Aku perlu berbicara dengan ibuku. Mungkin butuh waktu lama.

105
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:33,729
Pergilah.

106
00:08:35,269 --> 00:08:36,970
